description:
Danny discusses the Madison/Southern Charm/Very Cav*llari drama, then recaps this week's Real Housewives of Atlanta, which featured Kenya on a jet, panty gifts, and more.


After the Bravo stuff, Danny interviews singer/songwriter JP Saxe about his "If The World Was Ending" song, which is nominated for Song of the Year at the Grammys, and his career/musicianship.


RHOA: 8:33ish

JP Saxe Interview: 29:10ish
